00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:19.660
I'm just going to search for tigers labeled for reuse with modification.

00:05:19.660 --> 00:05:22.955
Then these are filtered down to the ones we can modify.

00:05:22.955 --> 00:05:27.050
But again, do click on the individual image and go to the website.

00:05:27.050 --> 00:05:29.690
Just double-check that the image is free to

00:05:29.690 --> 00:05:33.700
download and whether or not any attribution is required.

00:05:33.700 --> 00:05:38.599
Of course, you can find many more free and paid stock photography websites

00:05:38.599 --> 00:05:40.760
with a quick Google search,

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:44.190
but these are some great sites to get you started.
